org.clafer.ir.compiler

Class IrSolutionMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.clafer.ir.compiler.IrSolutionMap

  • public class IrSolutionMap
extends Object
    Maps IR non-constant variables to their translated Choco variables. The get<Type>Var methods fail on constants. The get<Type>Value methods handles constants, and is the preferred way of lookup.
    Author:
    jimmy
